-- Taesa Is in Talks to Buy Abengoa’s 50% Stake in Unisa
-- B y   K a r e n   E e u w e n s
-- 2012-03-16T13:07:34Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-03-16/taesa-is-in-talks-to-buy-abengoa-s-50-stake-in-unisa-correct-.html
(Corrects to say that Taesa is in talks to buy Abengoa’s
50% stake in Unisa.)  Transmissora Alianca de Energia
Eletrica SA, known as Taesa, said it’s in advanced talks to buy
Abengoa Concessoes Brasil Holding SA’s 50 percent stake in Uniao
de Transmissoras de Energia Eletrica SA, known as Unisa,
according to a regulatory filing.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Karen Eeuwens in London at 
